Who sold NCI stock? Who is selling NCI stock?

NCI's stock was sold by a variety of institutional investors in the last quarter, including Acadian Asset Management LLC, Dalton Greiner Hartman Maher & Co., Russell Investments Group Ltd. and James Investment Research Inc..  View Insider Buying and Selling for NCI.



Who bought NCI stock? Who is buying NCI stock?

NCI's stock was purchased by a variety of institutional investors in the last quarter, including Strs Ohio.  View Insider Buying and Selling for NCI.



How do I buy NCI stock? 

Shares of NCI can be purchased through any online brokerage account. Popular online brokerages include Vanguard Brokerage Services, TD Ameritrade, E*TRADE, Scottrade, Fidelity and Charles Schwab. 



What is NCI's stock price today?

One share of NCI stock can currently be purchased for approximately $19.93.


